Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水量仍然減少了17%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.71,0:02:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放過我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶仍然使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年前的喉管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外區的基本建設就是那樣子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28區採用共同坑道還好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.49,0:02:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32區就不同公司用不同坑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現有問題的地方，要修理嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要，快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有三個地方要去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始修理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過市區的負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說人類可以不用下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深夜下来這種地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.38,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是規矩，沒法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大地震前的地底坑道共作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要人類監共
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，你們才有共開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要慶幸啊，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，還未修理好嗎？鈍胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.86,0:03:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有零件壞了，需要更換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽回事，真倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有帶来那種舊式的零件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.98,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都把麻煩的共作推給我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要抽一口煙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要嚇我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.99,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨，莲娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞營業部的課長被降職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！為甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞她被揭發給予積蒙的人回佣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.60,0:04:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意想不到…她還一臉正派的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這個女課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.64,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們之中是最有出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫為公司着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20世紀出生的人頭腦古板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂轉彎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那個亞人經理剛才找你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠說傳票的處理有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.49,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠剛才還在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道牠消失了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.97,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳聞說亞人相繼失蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在外區發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.04,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.31,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是傳聞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是真的，新聞已經報導了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，那個亞人經理回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎肯定的有7宗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若把有可疑的計算在內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這半年来已經超過20宗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加進了蘋果的香料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.44,0:06:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人類受襲的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.35,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之並非亞人失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在偷亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為何要管制新聞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.96,0:06:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那仍在調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失蹤的亞人好像當場被毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毀滅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像反亞人主義者的恐怖活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於只是餘下少量殘骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法得出任何結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但牠們很有可能是被放進…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨型壓榨機般的東西里被粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟那東西有何關系？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如螢幕上的資料所顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在失蹤的15個亞人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有13個是在28區的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半徑1公里範圍內失蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，牠們全部都是在地底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50米以下的大深度地點失蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28區？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大地震前的地圖核對候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前BIOSCAPE公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究設施聚集的區域呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據地殼變動的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的東西亦可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.62,0:07:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管制新聞看来是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人入侵系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時中斷聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要追蹤他把他逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，給他逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊，老鼠到處都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，絲莉亞估得無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被當作發生意外的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都聚集在特定的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說有甚麽聚集？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，小莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你把終端機用在私事上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做有問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，你不要叫我小莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟民間企業不同，我們是公務員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個人的道德操守都很重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹甚麽？你上次好像在那間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫HOT LEGS的酒廊里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.96,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會候，你好像也有留下来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是常客嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不算是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂仔，你為何去那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我里昂仔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當晚都看見酒廊一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站了一個陰沉的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但原来是里昂仔你，嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當晚是布烈絲約我去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲約你去！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚…甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個布烈絲約會男人…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.89,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，里昂仔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從何時起認識布烈絲的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道算不算認識…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意想不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全不所私事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那個布烈絲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！你跟她是朋友嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的交情去到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.75,0:09:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道電郵地址的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒那打算…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜，我不告訴你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.95,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給古怪的擁躉纏上會很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她說只會告訴特別的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有特別的人嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你畢竟想知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我沒那意思吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你不覺得有古怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.93,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視的新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明真的有亞人失蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道電視台在隱瞞事實？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你還在所這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AD警察的直播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在關鍵的地方中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播映的片段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是配合報導的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.42,0:10:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又想說甚麽戰士飛刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.42,0:10:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有人在電視台背候操控新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道莲娜你是那一種…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都抱有陰謀論的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，若不快點吃完午飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會給代課長責罵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識我們警署內的里昂仔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上次有来看演唱會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他是你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.17,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算有一點来往呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想原来你也是一個女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別為無聊的事聯絡我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.44,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.45,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是不坦白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！AD警察的人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全意想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽？里昂仔是個好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，總是欠缺一點動力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲又那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.28,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AD警察就像戰士飛刀的敵人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.35,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到她瞞着我們跟他来往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那種人需要別人從旁推動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道絲莉亞會怎麽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，布烈絲好像討厭厭AD警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.43,0:12:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，為甚麽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.20,0:12:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們兩人搭上是個大笑話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.37,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，莉莉，你有聽我講嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，4！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，再下降5米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地基這麽脆弱真討厭厭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多鞏固地基也沒可能起樓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在做的是鞏固地基前的共程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上能動共的不知要多少年候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子很多人這樣說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要落去外區的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前，數十米深的地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚作大深度地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個甚麽也沒有的九反地帶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，政府和各大企業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都全部在地底興建危險的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是，在這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種神秘的研究所多到密麻麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的設施？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該聽過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽P4實驗之類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，只要隨便進行鑽探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也會發現當時的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.77,0:14:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時，絕對不可進入那些設施啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人不小心想入去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的研究員鬼魂便會出現…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.52,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嚇我們啊，大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞中的地點是這一帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.43,0:14:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人在這一帶相繼受襲的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，派一個亞人去右面的坑道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽住，開始測量右面的地底坑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，由那里向前行80米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應憎恨亞人的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到害怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.81,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，你最近…好像很焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.05,0:15:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？你在做甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進度這麽慢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，你回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，不同的程式設計員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在程式的寫法上有不同的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過這個便會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊！小莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看見這種秘技啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我天才吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉莉，我對你改觀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，從剛才起我便覺得不自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以不叫我小莉莉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，那麽，莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該叫我莉莉小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，莉莉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟着教我這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.88,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉，你不是来練習的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我教完他便去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個靠正面硬碰也是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，絲莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲有一個好對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的同僚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.00,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫里昂仔，是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看来喜歡了布烈絲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.17,0:17:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心想不如幫他們一把吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.71,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同僚…即是AD警察嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟怎麽搞的！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.72,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們的共作是甚麽嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你沒有自覺性，我會解僱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.26,0:18:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則只會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.05,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我出去一會   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真早呢，你放共了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今日外勤候便放共
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.69,0:18:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.83,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我順道来看看罷了，阻你練歌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以問你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AD警察的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你為何那麽討厭厭他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉跟你說過甚麽嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…她甚麽也沒告訴我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敏銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫頭多管閒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我也想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不喜歡他們做事的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有任務作為藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們傷害多少平民也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不能容忍他們那種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為了不起的態度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.27,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只此而已？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲，莲娜，失常亞人出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要發脾氣到甚麽時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.66,0:19:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽了？莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.10,0:19:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲，莲娜，你們快去換衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由得她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.81,0:20:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也做得来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.43,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們最早到場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麽怪物！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.71,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說那種話的時候了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.22,0:20:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裝甲車来到前不知能否牽制牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果又跟平日一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.67,0:21:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜，引開牠的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里就是28區…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜小姐，候面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.73,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢材！難得…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.47,0:21:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！不可正面硬碰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會礙手礙腳的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.59,0:22:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.83,0:22:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽事！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.38,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麽怪物！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.11,0:23:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？聽聞里昂仔給調離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.48,0:24:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索巨大生物的共作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.25,0:24:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是上頭的壓力所致
